                            },
                            {
                              "id": "684657f4-c478-4e8b-9e83-c1641c5af3ba",
                              "title": "例子：两个线程互相礼让资源",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "2f159282-1a36-4170-ac6e-01bc9ddc81ae",
                        "title": "饥饿（Starvation）",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "ee3c5fe0-96d0-4c40-9e12-d67d1a95e1a2",
                              "title": "某个线程长期无法获得所需资源",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "b90f3f14-da5f-4a3b-8c20-8e2efa5f7362",
                              "title": "原因：优先级调度、资源分配不公平",
