                      },
                      {
                        "id": "ad407e82-01d5-414d-84de-6300856f03cd",
                        "title": "通过`go`关键字启动",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "bbc28a11-1667-4d20-8505-e2e8b6f4f355",
                              "title": "```go\n// 基本用法\ngo func() {\n    fmt.Println(\"这是一个goroutine\")\n}()\n\n// 带参数\ngo func(id int) {\n    fmt.Printf(\"Goroutine %d\\n\", id)\n}(1)\n```",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      },
