                },
                {
                  "id": "b14e22be-f717-4e73-a3d7-cbcba51b2a1b",
                  "title": "2.2 Channel：goroutine通信管道",
                  "titleUnedited": false,
                  "children": {
                    "attached": [
                      {
                        "id": "dbcd0fa1-7bab-4779-a8e3-eb22822fdbd4",
                        "title": "核心概念",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "6c27c5af-768e-4c1d-a020-97f98052d878",
                              "title": "CSP（Communicating Sequential Processes）模型的核心",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "68455378-2681-42da-b105-3735b2fd497f",
                              "title": "\"不要通过共享内存来通信，而应该通过通信来共享内存\"",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "c6711f7d-942c-4d68-b8fe-522df45ca817",
                              "title": "类型安全，编译时检查",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "4501c33b-558a-4664-a961-242654c69c5e",
                        "title": "Channel的三组特性",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "7a0e8355-4c1c-4362-a9c3-545d6e734068",
                              "title": "1. 同步 vs 异步（通信模式）",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "417c4653-4d1a-4c76-9479-4d5afb098809",
                              "title": "2. 无缓冲 vs 有缓冲（实现方式）",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "a21d5707-6f56-4768-959c-34eedb239790",
                                    "title": "```go\nch1 := make(chan int)      // 无缓冲，必然同步\nch2 := make(chan int, 10)  // 有缓冲，条件异步\n\nch2 <- 1  // 异步（未满）\nch2 <- 2  // 异步（未满）\n// ... 放满后\nch2 <- 11 // 阻塞！满了，变成同步\n```",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "05edb561-530f-4760-8190-c746a8a2c09c",
                              "title": "3. 双向 vs 单向（权限控制）",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "2b1b3ff9-ba01-4dca-8179-6acec15772cf",
                                    "title": "```go\n// 创建：永远双向\norderQueue := make(chan Order, 100)\n\n// 使用：传参时限制权限（编译器自动转换）\nfunc producer(ch chan<- Order, order Order) { ch <- order }  // 只能发\nfunc consumer(ch <-chan Order) { order := <-ch; _ = order }  // 只能收\n\ngo producer(orderQueue, Order{ID: 1})  // 自动转成只发送\ngo consumer(orderQueue)                 // 自动转成只接收\n```",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "7d41d578-4a2e-47d4-8a84-22ea13719339",
                              "title": "实用矩阵：缓冲 × 方向（共9种组合）",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "fa43c67a-83fc-4728-b69e-a549a0b22db2",
                  "title": "2.3 同步原语",
                  "titleUnedited": false,
                  "children": {
                    "attached": [
                      {
                        "id": "01cc890c-4b64-4039-a630-075ad9347953",
                        "title": "sync.WaitGroup —— 等所有人到齐",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "8c998fb6-c350-4ebf-8e52-0000f6435fdc",
                              "title": "发起团购，需要凑齐5人才能发货",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "097ccc44-47b6-4e86-b55c-c76ab7f1a66b",
                              "title": "每有一人下单，计数+1；每有一人付款完成，计数-1",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "f1720a1f-e354-4da7-aedc-ca26f16ca9ae",
                              "title": "主线程等待（Wait），直到计数归零才发货",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "221f7a76-7d59-44cb-97a8-715f7b29f846",
                                    "title": "```go\nvar wg sync.WaitGroup\nwg.Add(3) // 需要等3个任务\n\nfor i := 0; i < 3; i++ {\n    go func(id int) {\n        defer wg.Done() // 完成一个，计数-1\n        处理订单(id)\n    }(i)\n}\n\nwg.Wait() // 等3个都完成，再继续\nfmt.Println(\"所有订单处理完毕\")\n```",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "6cf6d76d-0784-4060-8d70-73eaccefa1a2",
                        "title": "sync.Mutex —— 互斥锁",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "9edc2693-cff9-412f-9165-246a6e770355",
                              "title": "试衣间一次只能进一个人",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "a7ed9a20-8425-4dc6-88e2-87a49593b358",
                              "title": "进去要锁门（Lock），出来要开门（Unlock）",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "3022f606-552a-430f-b455-05d14bdd33a1",
                              "title": "其他人在门口排队等",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "c206fd96-ba70-449a-89b4-e58c448989e6",
                                    "title": "```go\nvar mu sync.Mutex\nvar 库存 = 100\n\nfunc 扣库存() {\n    mu.Lock()         // 锁门\n    defer mu.Unlock() // 确保出来时开门\n    库存--            // 安全修改\n}\n\n// 100个goroutine同时扣库存，不会超卖\n```",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "925e6363-2285-4d48-8e2c-90cb377e1ac6",
                        "title": "sync.RWMutex —— 读写锁",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "81826368-8cdf-4276-b1f8-ea1f785c87fc",
                              "title": "看商品详情（读）：可以很多人同时看",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "4b95abb2-898e-4cf8-bdf8-1a099f48e60a",
                              "title": "改商品价格（写）：必须清场，改完才能继续看",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "792b385a-c14e-4f73-a2a0-a99eae7b96b7",
                              "title": "读多写少时，比Mutex效率高",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "249c42df-c5e2-43be-b542-07aa909dfaeb",
                                    "title": "```go\nvar rwmu sync.RWMutex\nvar 商品价格 = 99.00\n\nfunc 查看价格() float64 {\n    rwmu.RLock()         // 读锁，可多人同时读\n    defer rwmu.RUnlock()\n    return 商品价格\n}\n\nfunc 修改价格(新价格 float64) {\n    rwmu.Lock()          // 写锁，独占\n    defer rwmu.Unlock()\n    商品价格 = 新价格\n}\n```",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "34f57495-2b72-492c-9932-709fa48f567e",
                        "title": "context —— 超时与取消",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "24970f43-78e9-433d-a4ce-26c497df86a9",
                              "title": "下单时设置\"30分钟超时\"",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "4d6ddcc2-5441-47f8-961e-4e4b306ddeea",
                              "title": "骑手（goroutine）随时检查是否超时或被取消",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "1e1fdfee-a10e-494c-aa9b-cff82ca5a05c",
                              "title": "超时了就不送了，及时止损",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "a81b0543-d1af-4a2c-86ea-a1772d52daea",
                                    "title": "```go\n// 设置2秒超时\nctx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(context.Background(), 2*time.Second)\ndefer cancel() // 别忘了释放资源\n\nselect {\ncase 结果 := <-处理订单():\n    fmt.Println(\"订单完成:\", 结果)\ncase <-ctx.Done():\n    fmt.Println(\"超时了:\", ctx.Err()) // 及时止损\n}\n```",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "554d06ec-5830-443a-a04e-200a497cf9e8",
                              "title": "调用外部API，防止卡死 → WithTimeout",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "49d0a83e-3c81-418a-a771-efb11288ad22",
                              "title": "用户取消操作，通知所有goroutine停止 → WithCancel",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "27776f63-d7df-4890-b775-babc021aa789",
                              "title": "请求链路追踪，传递请求ID → WithValue",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "fc9b62ba-2faa-4649-b925-32b6266702b5",
                        "title": "同步原语选择矩阵",
                        "titleUnedited": false
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "0a763c0e-acb3-4093-939b-97cb1edbb609",
                  "title": "2.4 select语句：多路复用",
                  "titleUnedited": false,
                  "children": {
                    "attached": [
                      {
                        "id": "3b965223-2ab2-48fe-8388-d93b4466bda6",
                        "title": "同时监听多个channel操作",
                        "titleUnedited": false
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "e80bb225-394d-4b22-8462-323910650564",
                        "title": "非阻塞通信基础",
                        "titleUnedited": false
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "661153e7-d577-4216-ba83-8a3a7073c644",
                        "title": "实现超时、重试等模式",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "662c2fb3-ffb6-499a-982b-521f086aec5c",
                              "title": "```go\nselect {\ncase data := <-ch1:\n    fmt.Println(\"Received from ch1:\", data)\ncase <-time.After(1 * time.Second):\n    fmt.Println(\"Timeout\")\ncase ch2 <- 42:\n    fmt.Println(\"Sent to ch2\")\ndefault:\n    fmt.Println(\"No communication ready\")\n}\n```",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "e38f7374-58b3-4156-a1f6-fd3ce3b72f74",
            "title": "第三部分：多线程问题和线程不安全",
            "titleUnedited": false,
            "children": {
              "attached": [
                {
                  "id": "e7732b77-c81c-4217-b073-02717197b91e",
                  "title": "3.1 线程不安全的三大特性",
                  "titleUnedited": false,
                  "children": {
                    "attached": [
                      {
                        "id": "3ffa2751-af11-47fc-9778-d1faacf6be8b",
                        "title": "3.1.1 可见性（Visibility）",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "abb3800b-de51-47d4-8710-d2b4bf100685",
                              "title": "问题：一个goroutine修改共享变量后，其他goroutine可能看不到最新值，因为：",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "cfa46647-fe6d-44f7-919c-95c30b14d529",
                                    "title": "CPU缓存不一致（MESI协议）",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
                                  },
                                  {
                                    "id": "cccf0524-1e79-41ee-8af2-9317a4fddaea",
                                    "title": "编译器优化重排序",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
                                  },
                                  {
                                    "id": "fcb42fc4-0bd9-434b-a3f0-df6c2f42836a",
                                    "title": "处理器指令重排序",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "18c19f2e-e49f-4325-b7a1-a69b631bb4c9",
                              "title": "Go解决方案：",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "fcbc7839-c32a-4498-a79d-d1f83595f420",
                                    "title": "sync.Mutex：锁操作包含内存屏障，保证可见性",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
                                  },
                                  {
                                    "id": "c80c20b1-7e93-4c9e-a6fe-1ed8767264b3",
                                    "title": "sync/atomic：原子操作，包含内存屏障",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
                                  },
                                  {
                                    "id": "bebc7a69-d700-4a0e-923f-90a4f6d90f4a",
                                    "title": "Channel：通过channel通信天然保证可见性",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
                                  },
                                  {
                                    "id": "e174386c-ff9a-4f1e-9d25-ce044e07ac06",
                                    "title": "sync.Once：保证初始化操作只执行一次",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "44218170-40f0-4bc2-bfdb-70159ea8cf21",
                              "title": "(代码块)",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "8891e953-a8e7-4ff1-af8d-dd8a2001dd3d",
                                    "title": "(代码块)",
                                    "titleUnedited": false,
                                    "children": {
                                      "attached": [
                                        {
                                          "id": "40b094a4-dd97-4cff-b715-b7b1099cf622",
                                          "title": "```go\nvar (\n    mu      sync.Mutex\n    flag    bool\n    counter int\n)\n\n// 通过锁保证可见性\nfunc writer() {\n    mu.Lock()\n    counter = 10\n    flag = true\n    mu.Unlock()\n}\n\nfunc reader() {\n    mu.Lock()\n    defer mu.Unlock()\n    if flag {\n        fmt.Println(counter) // 保证看到最新值\n    }\n}\n```",
                                          "titleUnedited": false
                                        }
                                      ]
                                    }
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "b8f0ab8d-1bd0-4e5d-a347-98adc2719dce",
                        "title": "3.1.2 原子性（Atomicity）",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "6dd582fd-2b87-4ed0-8020-9f74d3ec0ca8",
                              "title": "问题：复合操作（如`counter++`）被中断，导致数据不一致：",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "478c3b22-cbfd-48c8-aa25-444d790eeef8",
                                    "title": "读取counter值到CPU寄存器",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
                                  },
                                  {
                                    "id": "5989c22c-474e-48b5-8de0-93d2c5cab87a",
                                    "title": "寄存器值+1",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
                                  },
                                  {
                                    "id": "92ddf757-006c-45ba-a089-03b75fc027b2",
                                    "title": "写回counter",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "837ab25d-e200-455c-ae3b-decc67668066",
                              "title": "Go解决方案：",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "3317801e-658f-41d3-ae56-3d0e229a6c29",
                                    "title": "sync.Mutex：锁保护整个操作",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
                                  },
                                  {
                                    "id": "dfa5b6a7-eda5-40c3-9978-711561bd43b1",
                                    "title": "sync/atomic：原子操作（AddInt32, CompareAndSwap等）",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
                                  },
                                  {
                                    "id": "03a3e180-47ed-4406-b6f7-6715ea83de27",
                                    "title": "sync.Map：并发安全的map",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
                                  },
                                  {
                                    "id": "c61099e3-59c6-4dc9-93e4-042e7a06940c",
                                    "title": "(代码块)",
                                    "titleUnedited": false,
                                    "children": {
                                      "attached": [
                                        {
                                          "id": "716f5b5e-f82c-422e-88d0-7eb6deea6ce3",
                                          "title": "(代码块)",
                                          "titleUnedited": false,
                                          "children": {
                                            "attached": [
                                              {
                                                "id": "b8b6f8fd-5390-441e-a2d5-586c049fb929",
                                                "title": "```go\nvar counter int32\n\n// 原子操作\nfunc atomicIncrement() {\n    atomic.AddInt32(&counter, 1)\n}\n\n// CAS操作\nfunc compareAndSwap(old, new int32) bool {\n    return atomic.CompareAndSwapInt32(&counter, old, new)\n}\n```",
                                                "titleUnedited": false
                                              }
                                            ]
                                          }
                                        }
                                      ]
                                    }
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "f29c1da3-dcca-4eea-873b-2cd01fb82a4a",
                        "title": "3.1.3 有序性（Orderliness）",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "4b661bd0-0bd8-4d79-beaf-ce7961af1e50",
                              "title": "仓库发货（写数据） happens-before 用户签收（读数据）",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "8aab827a-11d4-4d11-93fe-e2af94ba500e",
                              "title": "只有确认发货了，用户才能签收到正确的商品",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "4764f4d2-04ed-4dbf-8e64-fe319f1c0691",
                              "title": "问题：编译器和处理器为了优化性能，可能重排序指令，导致程序行为不符合预期。",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "96386373-f20f-420d-b453-71a1fe643046",
                                    "title": "Go内存模型保证的happens-before关系：",
                                    "titleUnedited": false,
                                    "children": {
                                      "attached": [
                                        {
                                          "id": "5dfdbb46-ebdf-49a4-a9fa-ce0e0f7e6f72",
                                          "title": "单个goroutine内，按程序顺序happens-before",
                                          "titleUnedited": false
                                        },
                                        {
                                          "id": "b295a378-a2c3-4e13-b415-c8dda79a65b7",
                                          "title": "无缓冲channel：发送完成 happens-before 接收完成",
                                          "titleUnedited": false
                                        },
                                        {
                                          "id": "61d68631-8d6f-4c3c-ac38-e6817d20509e",
                                          "title": "有缓冲channel：第k次接收完成 happens-before 第k+C次发送完成（C为缓冲大小）",
                                          "titleUnedited": false
                                        },
                                        {
                                          "id": "93a099e1-ffb8-4dd9-b502-6f1d4e8281d2",
                                          "title": "channel关闭：close happens-before 接收方收到零值",
                                          "titleUnedited": false
                                        },
                                        {
                                          "id": "72d7580f-e21a-4683-881a-71087261bf33",
                                          "title": "锁操作：解锁happens-before后续加锁",
                                          "titleUnedited": false
                                        },
                                        {
                                          "id": "bd4cab03-2fb5-4d71-8cf2-129a33a35175",
                                          "title": "sync.Once.Do：初始化happens-before后续调用",
                                          "titleUnedited": false
                                        }
                                      ]
                                    }
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "f05927b9-01d7-4657-b3e1-3bc7a6dbc618",
                              "title": "Go解决方案：",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "98760fb2-c3a9-4cb2-b3da-cbdf80d6d2ed",
                                    "title": "Channel：通过通信保证顺序",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
                                  },
                                  {
                                    "id": "1ec21a8e-9bd7-4098-98fd-0699e7866ee6",
                                    "title": "sync.WaitGroup：等待特定操作完成后再继续",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
                                  },
                                  {
                                    "id": "83e509ac-dd4d-4498-9d82-5783dd99fdbd",
                                    "title": "sync.Once：保证初始化顺序",
                                    "titleUnedited": false,
                                    "children": {
                                      "attached": [
                                        {
                                          "id": "c061b069-86b1-4502-a5d3-401c3a7e6412",
                                          "title": "```go\n// 错误示例：没有happens-before保证（存在数据竞争）\nvar data = 0\nvar ready = false\n\ngo func() {\n    data = 42      // 写数据\n    ready = true   // 可能被重排序到data=42之前！\n}()\n\n// 问题1：主goroutine可能在子goroutine启动前就检查ready\n// 问题2：即使用循环等待，也可能因编译器优化永远看不到ready=true\n// 问题3：即使看到ready=true，data也可能因重排序仍为0\nfor !ready {\n    // 忙等待（本身也有问题，仅作演示）\n}\nfmt.Println(data) // 可能打印0！\n\n// 正确做法：用channel建立happens-before关系\ndone := make(chan bool)\n\ngo func() {\n    data = 42\n    done <- true  // 发送 happens-before 接收\n}()\n\n<-done           // 接收\nfmt.Println(data) // 保证打印42\n```",
                                          "titleUnedited": false
                                        }
                                      ]
                                    }
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "6e82cc21-e023-4f94-88ca-32362395ae58",
                  "title": "3.2 隔离性（Isolation）",
                  "titleUnedited": false,
                  "children": {
                    "attached": [
                      {
                        "id": "d41f66ab-8b48-4c57-8f4e-7f4b1eef0e12",
                        "title": "问题：不同goroutine之间数据相互干扰，特别是局部状态。",
                        "titleUnedited": false
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "d063d8ee-22fc-467a-8e5f-4a12fe7428b0",
                        "title": "Go解决方案：",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "42949424-55ea-4e90-b33d-59e33e36e479",
                              "title": "Goroutine局部变量：每个goroutine有自己的栈空间",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "1dde3e36-f9a8-4c38-a005-15d77f0a402f",
                              "title": "context.Value：请求范围数据隔离",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "ae9e79c2-4b2f-4483-a9d6-0e99d0b02266",
                              "title": "sync.Pool：对象池，减少GC压力，但注意隔离性",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "44b078ad-e9d2-4772-a886-5bb4bda844ae",
                              "title": "(代码块)",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "cbbea8cd-8d17-441a-b8a5-29b057d22984",
                                    "title": "(代码块)",
                                    "titleUnedited": false,
                                    "children": {
                                      "attached": [
                                        {
                                          "id": "a0098f30-53af-4fd7-8296-2fac237a722a",
                                          "title": "```go\n// context.Value隔离\ntype keyType string\nconst requestIDKey keyType = \"request_id\"\n\nfunc handleRequest(ctx context.Context) {\n    requestID := ctx.Value(requestIDKey).(string)\n    // 每个请求有自己的requestID\n}\n```",
