                            {
                              "id": "2d5b94b4-f0b7-47cb-9a7c-c262f862cd8d",
                              "title": "缓冲区大小：根据生产者-消费者速度差异设置",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "55b8d9a5-0149-432e-9113-3b3dd1817c74",
                              "title": "避免channel泄漏",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "b889c66d-911c-43a4-8328-1d69fcc8088b",
                              "title": "(代码块)",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "0ed427cc-edd8-4fcf-b2ac-413f53e670cd",
                                    "title": "(代码块)",
                                    "titleUnedited": false,
                                    "children": {
                                      "attached": [
                                        {
                                          "id": "735a9e24-d540-45de-82a8-a82bd9eb2829",
                                          "title": "```go\n// 坏：可能泄漏\nfunc badWorker() {\n    ch := make(chan int)\n    go func() {\n        for i := 0; i < 10; i++ {\n            ch <- i\n        }\n    }()\n    \n    for v := range ch {\n        fmt.Println(v)\n    }\n    // ch未关闭，goroutine可能阻塞\n}\n\n// 好：确保关闭\nfunc goodWorker() {\n    ch := make(chan int)\n    go func() {\n        defer close(ch) // 确保关闭\n        for i := 0; i < 10; i++ {\n            ch <- i\n        }\n    }()\n    \n    for v := range ch {\n        fmt.Println(v)\n    }\n}\n```",
                                          "titleUnedited": false
                                        }
                                      ]
                                    }
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            }
