                      {
                        "id": "db0523c9-a8c9-488a-a12c-fe6221ce06d4",
                        "title": "4.2.3 内存优化",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "02abd14f-1c44-405e-a4c3-d14ff2cacd41",
                              "title": "使用sync.Pool复用对象",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "2f2409e5-5470-4347-9c5d-a8dc903ce545",
                                    "title": "```go\nvar bufferPool = sync.Pool{\n    New: func() interface{} {\n        return make([]byte, 4096)\n    },\n}\n\nfunc processRequest(conn net.Conn) {\n    buf := bufferPool.Get().([]byte)\n    defer func() {\n        // 重置buffer防止数据泄露（重要！）\n        clear(buf) // Go 1.21+，或用 for i := range buf { buf[i] = 0 }\n        bufferPool.Put(buf)\n    }()\n    n, err := conn.Read(buf)\n    if err != nil {\n        return\n    }\n    // 处理 buf[:n]\n    _ = n\n}\n```",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "4c834ddb-530c-443d-8967-f3fe7001b6c7",
                        "title": "4.2.4 避免闭包捕获",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
