                                    "id": "1511cf2e-06ba-4324-a4d3-d30077521f8d",
                                    "title": "```go\n// 错误示例（Go 1.21及以前版本）\nfor i := 1; i <= 3; i++ {\n    go func() {\n        fmt.Println(\"处理订单\", i) // 可能全打印4！\n    }()\n}\n\n// 正确做法：传参复制值\nfor i := 1; i <= 3; i++ {\n    go func(orderID int) {  // 参数传值，复制一份\n        fmt.Println(\"处理订单\", orderID)\n    }(i)\n}\n```",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
