                {
                  "id": "0bcf2c26-09d9-4e40-a509-d21a38e2fe7b",
                  "title": "5.2 Go中的死锁场景",
                  "titleUnedited": false,
                  "children": {
                    "attached": [
                      {
                        "id": "e972e49a-b696-4bc8-a2df-5534d0be4a31",
                        "title": "5.2.1 Channel死锁",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "0cb37a85-10e1-4a6a-a270-b301d172a3a5",
                              "title": "(代码块)",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "1b22ac6e-4ed4-46c5-b3cd-1e93f237e35a",
                                    "title": "(代码块)",
                                    "titleUnedited": false,
                                    "children": {
                                      "attached": [
                                        {
                                          "id": "f0bdc765-2992-4411-b639-9db306cedda7",
                                          "title": "```go\n// 无缓冲channel死锁：主goroutine发送，无人接收\nfunc channelDeadlock1() {\n    ch := make(chan int)\n    ch <- 1 // 主goroutine阻塞，无其他goroutine接收\n    // fatal error: all goroutines are asleep - deadlock!\n}\n\n// 无缓冲channel死锁：有发送者，无接收者\nfunc channelDeadlock2() {\n    ch := make(chan int)\n    go func() {\n        ch <- 42 // goroutine尝试发送，阻塞等待接收者\n    }()\n    ch <- 1 // 主goroutine也发送，两个发送者都阻塞，无人接收\n}\n```",
                                          "titleUnedited": false
                                        }
                                      ]
                                    }
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "faec476b-fc7d-40e4-b90f-98fffda8f3fd",
                        "title": "5.2.2 Mutex死锁",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "4e35b6cf-a15f-4ed5-8632-21ef9e516ee0",
                              "title": "(代码块)",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "84b8e28f-f329-410e-b72e-748e618dfc66",
                                    "title": "(代码块)",
                                    "titleUnedited": false,
                                    "children": {
                                      "attached": [
                                        {
                                          "id": "5625a4e0-9abf-4aba-aac5-1e8076708b30",
                                          "title": "```go\n// 交叉锁死锁\nfunc mutexDeadlock() {\n    var mu1, mu2 sync.Mutex\n    \n    go func() {\n        mu1.Lock()\n        defer mu1.Unlock()\n        \n        time.Sleep(100 * time.Millisecond)\n        \n        mu2.Lock() // 等待mu2\n        defer mu2.Unlock()\n    }()\n    \n    mu2.Lock()\n    defer mu2.Unlock()\n    \n    time.Sleep(50 * time.Millisecond)\n    \n    mu1.Lock() // 等待mu1，死锁\n    defer mu1.Unlock()\n}\n```",
                                          "titleUnedited": false
                                        }
                                      ]
                                    }
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "742d207f-9f4e-41ed-b7a4-b3135cfc132b",
                        "title": "5.2.3 WaitGroup误用（panic与死锁）",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "834c62ff-8741-4ef2-96e6-487a2f2a7868",
                              "title": "(代码块)",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "d5cd03ce-3916-4577-b626-a319ad5270c6",
                                    "title": "(代码块)",
                                    "titleUnedited": false,
                                    "children": {
                                      "attached": [
                                        {
                                          "id": "468b1043-292f-4278-af3f-5e682bc6c093",
                                          "title": "```go\n// WaitGroup计数错误导致panic\nfunc wgPanic() {\n    var wg sync.WaitGroup\n    wg.Add(1)\n    go func() { wg.Done() }()\n    go func() { wg.Done() }() // panic: negative WaitGroup counter\n    wg.Wait()\n}\n\n// WaitGroup真正的死锁\nfunc wgDeadlock() {\n    var wg sync.WaitGroup\n    wg.Add(1)\n    wg.Wait() // 没有goroutine调用Done()，永远阻塞\n}\n```",
                                          "titleUnedited": false
                                        }
                                      ]
                                    }
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  }
