                {
                  "id": "9c233655-3077-441b-9eff-6ba0ced90d11",
                  "title": "5.4 死锁解决方案",
                  "titleUnedited": false,
                  "children": {
                    "attached": [
                      {
                        "id": "d2faeee6-8637-4b1d-aa56-50982e2c512c",
                        "title": "5.4.1 预防策略",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "fcb05f84-813f-448f-ae3e-e3cc9f1b9e17",
                              "title": "1. 按固定顺序获取锁",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "4730ba98-c6ab-4747-b61b-8ddd7318c446",
                                    "title": "(代码块)",
                                    "titleUnedited": false,
                                    "children": {
                                      "attached": [
                                        {
                                          "id": "e0bcc873-878d-4145-92c5-f5742f7df74d",
                                          "title": "(代码块)",
                                          "titleUnedited": false,
                                          "children": {
                                            "attached": [
                                              {
                                                "id": "68f79d14-79fa-4416-8f51-87959a69de70",
                                                "title": "```go\n// 好：总是按相同顺序获取锁\nfunc safeOperation() {\n    mu1.Lock()\n    defer mu1.Unlock()\n    \n    mu2.Lock()\n    defer mu2.Unlock()\n    \n    // 操作共享资源\n}\n```",
                                                "titleUnedited": false
                                              }
                                            ]
                                          }
                                        }
                                      ]
                                    }
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "f9be9dec-2b15-43ed-8079-df99c961428b",
                              "title": "2. 超时机制（Go 1.18+ TryLock）",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "4bc06297-7372-4814-aa92-e02e3033260f",
                                    "title": "(代码块)",
                                    "titleUnedited": false,
                                    "children": {
                                      "attached": [
                                        {
                                          "id": "6b331f07-87be-4dee-bffe-626a9f2022be",
                                          "title": "(代码块)",
                                          "titleUnedited": false,
                                          "children": {
                                            "attached": [
                                              {
                                                "id": "d5f87877-6b71-49a1-a04a-7ca1a547f1d0",
                                                "title": "```go\n// Go 1.18+ 使用TryLock实现超时获取锁\n// 注意：这是自旋等待的简化示例，生产环境建议使用channel+context或semaphore\nfunc tryLockWithTimeout(mu *sync.Mutex, timeout time.Duration) bool {\n    deadline := time.Now().Add(timeout)\n    for time.Now().Before(deadline) {\n        if mu.TryLock() {\n            return true\n        }\n        time.Sleep(time.Millisecond) // 间隔可根据场景调整\n    }\n    return false\n}\n\n// 使用\nif tryLockWithTimeout(&mu, 100*time.Millisecond) {\n    defer mu.Unlock()\n    // 执行操作\n} else {\n    fmt.Println(\"获取锁超时\")\n}\n```",
                                                "titleUnedited": false
                                              }
                                            ]
                                          }
                                        }
                                      ]
                                    }
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "ff927202-f863-4b05-8683-0da9f8f6ea15",
                              "title": "3. 使用channel限制并发",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "dc10d183-9aae-433a-b9ed-1aad51129e3e",
                                    "title": "(代码块)",
                                    "titleUnedited": false,
                                    "children": {
                                      "attached": [
                                        {
                                          "id": "97c5900e-baec-4dd5-bcea-24c2e6760a11",
                                          "title": "(代码块)",
                                          "titleUnedited": false,
                                          "children": {
                                            "attached": [
                                              {
                                                "id": "87a67731-8465-4cbc-98c9-bfd262d88c81",
                                                "title": "```go\nfunc workerPoolWithTimeout() {\n    jobs := make(chan Job, 100)\n    results := make(chan Result, 100)\n    maxWorkers := runtime.NumCPU()\n    \n    for i := 0; i < maxWorkers; i++ {\n        go worker(jobs, results)\n    }\n    \n    // 提交任务\n    for i := 0; i < 100; i++ {\n        select {\n        case jobs <- Job{i}:\n            fmt.Printf(\"Submitted job %d\\n\", i)\n        case <-time.After(10 * time.Millisecond):\n            fmt.Printf(\"Job %d timeout, skipping\\n\", i)\n        }\n    }\n}\n```",
                                                "titleUnedited": false
                                              }
                                            ]
                                          }
                                        }
                                      ]
                                    }
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            }
                          ]
                        }
