                      {
                        "id": "eec79e4d-fbc8-4c15-86a3-175406aa70df",
                        "title": "5.4.3 恢复策略",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "dac29657-b564-46d4-a746-a739b0ce10e5",
                              "title": "1. 超时取消（避免goroutine泄漏）",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "debc9f8c-06ae-405d-89fb-f94e1f17904d",
                                    "title": "(代码块)",
                                    "titleUnedited": false,
                                    "children": {
                                      "attached": [
                                        {
                                          "id": "7984528f-0ee0-4ff9-a501-53caab9ef660",
                                          "title": "(代码块)",
                                          "titleUnedited": false,
                                          "children": {
                                            "attached": [
                                              {
                                                "id": "6d83aafc-001e-40a2-b647-5dd80ef8836b",
                                                "title": "```go\nfunc operationWithTimeout() {\n    ctx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(context.Background(), 2*time.Second)\n    defer cancel()\n    \n    resultChan := make(chan string, 1) // 缓冲channel防止泄漏\n    go func() {\n        time.Sleep(3 * time.Second)\n        select {\n        case resultChan <- \"result\":\n        case <-ctx.Done(): // 超时则直接返回\n        }\n    }()\n    \n    select {\n    case result := <-resultChan:\n        fmt.Println(result)\n    case <-ctx.Done():\n        fmt.Println(\"Operation timed out:\", ctx.Err())\n    }\n}\n```",
                                                "titleUnedited": false
                                              }
                                            ]
                                          }
                                        }
                                      ]
                                    }
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "7a657355-a324-49cd-aca8-e3520bdd4429",
                              "title": "2. 优雅降级",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "c063a544-08e1-4cd0-be96-bb9500670c54",
                                    "title": "(代码块)",
                                    "titleUnedited": false,
                                    "children": {
                                      "attached": [
                                        {
                                          "id": "d1bb92e6-0752-45e2-8df4-c23ab1dd9fb7",
                                          "title": "(代码块)",
                                          "titleUnedited": false,
                                          "children": {
                                            "attached": [
                                              {
                                                "id": "d5d92e33-f23b-40f3-bc59-8863e166c3db",
                                                "title": "```go\nfunc gracefulDegradation() {\n    ctx, cancel := context.WithCancel(context.Background())\n    defer cancel()\n    \n    go monitorSystemHealth(ctx, func() {\n        // 系统不健康时触发降级\n        cancel()\n    })\n    \n    select {\n    case <-doImportantWork(ctx):\n        fmt.Println(\"Work completed successfully\")\n    case <-ctx.Done():\n        fmt.Println(\"System degraded, skipping non-critical work\")\n        // 执行降级逻辑\n    }\n}\n```",
                                                "titleUnedited": false
                                              }
                                            ]
                                          }
                                        }
                                      ]
                                    }
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "22722ce1-ca35-4c1c-aea5-2285cf062783",
                  "title": "5.5 Go特色死锁解决方案",
                  "titleUnedited": false,
                  "children": {
                    "attached": [
                      {
                        "id": "723c6ff4-6cdd-41a3-82de-88b7bec43c2b",
                        "title": "5.5.1 使用select default避免阻塞",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "44267e65-cc7c-4153-936f-07c460ce7c71",
                              "title": "(代码块)",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "d27cb8c7-2c42-415b-8168-1a442441f5a4",
                                    "title": "(代码块)",
                                    "titleUnedited": false,
                                    "children": {
                                      "attached": [
                                        {
                                          "id": "e3b555bb-bf03-4bb7-b923-b31685b92d8e",
                                          "title": "```go\n// 好：使用default避免永久阻塞\nfunc nonBlockingSelect() {\n    ch := make(chan int)\n    \n    go func() {\n        time.Sleep(100 * time.Millisecond)\n        ch <- 42\n    }()\n    \n    select {\n    case val := <-ch:\n        fmt.Println(\"Received:\", val)\n    default:\n        fmt.Println(\"No data available, continuing...\")\n    }\n}\n```",
                                          "titleUnedited": false
                                        }
                                      ]
                                    }
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "0bc127e3-89fa-4f1b-8566-54781b0fca41",
                        "title": "5.5.2 Context取消传播",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "4681eacc-adcc-4297-9b6d-23066fd3309d",
                              "title": "(代码块)",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "9fe2374d-5790-427c-bf8f-b2dc94ed4569",
                                    "title": "(代码块)",
                                    "titleUnedited": false,
                                    "children": {
                                      "attached": [
                                        {
                                          "id": "07e7ed46-811d-4902-9b8f-3dee61b06010",
                                          "title": "```go\n// 通过context传播取消信号\nfunc contextCancellation() {\n    ctx, cancel := context.WithCancel(context.Background())\n    \n    // 启动多个goroutine\n    for i := 0; i < 5; i++ {\n        go func(id int) {\n            select {\n            case <-time.After(time.Duration(id) * time.Second):\n                fmt.Printf(\"Worker %d completed\\n\", id)\n            case <-ctx.Done():\n                fmt.Printf(\"Worker %d cancelled: %v\\n\", id, ctx.Err())\n            }\n        }(i)\n    }\n    \n    // 2秒后取消所有\n    time.Sleep(2 * time.Second)\n    cancel()\n}\n```",
                                          "titleUnedited": false
                                        }
                                      ]
                                    }
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "ed565766-f1e0-4fff-a2c5-81b09ddd7dde",
                        "title": "5.5.3 使用errgroup简化错误处理",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "a545bdab-d0f1-4504-96b6-1cd326394c45",
                              "title": "(代码块)",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "398279e4-f8eb-46d7-9fe5-e47a001d9889",
                                    "title": "(代码块)",
                                    "titleUnedited": false,
                                    "children": {
                                      "attached": [
                                        {
                                          "id": "77fd4653-93da-485a-bf3a-135d66893809",
                                          "title": "```go\nimport \"golang.org/x/sync/errgroup\"\n\nfunc errgroupExample() {\n    var g errgroup.Group\n    \n    // 启动多个goroutine\n    for i := 0; i < 5; i++ {\n        i := i // Go 1.21及之前需要此行避免闭包捕获问题，Go 1.22+可省略\n        g.Go(func() error {\n            if i == 3 {\n                return fmt.Errorf(\"error in worker %d\", i)\n            }\n            fmt.Printf(\"Worker %d started\\n\", i)\n            time.Sleep(time.Duration(i) * 100 * time.Millisecond)\n            fmt.Printf(\"Worker %d finished\\n\", i)\n            return nil\n        })\n    }\n    \n    // 等待所有完成或返回第一个错误\n    // 注意：需用errgroup.WithContext(ctx)创建才能自动取消其他goroutine\n    if err := g.Wait(); err != nil {\n        fmt.Printf(\"Group error: %v\\n\", err)\n    }\n}\n```",
                                          "titleUnedited": false
                                        }
                                      ]
                                    }
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "05a0992d-3335-481a-af97-7df9dd00961e",
            "title": "总结",
            "titleUnedited": false,
            "children": {
              "attached": [
                {
                  "id": "734d41aa-8384-4f14-9d9d-eb6b625812a8",
                  "title": "Go的并发模型通过goroutine和channel提供了一种简单而强大的并发编程方式。理解操作系统层面的多线程知识有助于更好地掌握Go的并发设计。通过遵循最佳实践，避免常见的并发陷阱，可以构建出高性能、高可靠的并发系统。",
                  "titleUnedited": false
                },
                {
                  "id": "6de0d950-48e8-4099-b829-cecf564164ca",
                  "title": "Go并发的核心哲学是：\"不要通过共享内存来通信，而应该通过通信来共享内存\"。这一原则贯穿于整个Go并发设计，使得并发编程变得更加简单和安全。",
                  "titleUnedited": false
                }
              ]
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "5cad2833-e3f0-46e3-9b42-4d587c0d4159",
            "title": "附录：并发编程词汇表",
            "titleUnedited": false,
            "children": {
              "attached": [
                {
                  "id": "4f45a007-1bcb-42d3-af06-0ec52989636d",
                  "title": "基础概念",
