                {
                  "id": "fc26ae9d-8f41-4739-95f9-c1d9a1828894",
                  "title": "缩写对照",
                  "titleUnedited": false
                },
                {
                  "id": "d73e3ca4-88e7-4c9f-a74c-fdb66641216a",
                  "title": "Java 锁概念与 Go 对照",
                  "titleUnedited": false,
                  "children": {
                    "attached": [
                      {
                        "id": "a7e6154d-77cf-497e-9c40-3eb54ff6fb00",
                        "title": "概念对照总表",
                        "titleUnedited": false
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "313aacad-34e2-4c28-8757-ed5155218d8e",
                        "title": "1. 重量级锁 vs 轻量级锁",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "eaaea5a0-c4f1-4b45-a329-3a05f48a43e1",
                              "title": "```\n无锁 → 偏向锁 → 轻量级锁 → 重量级锁\n       ↑          ↑           ↑\n    无竞争     CAS失败     自旋失败\n```",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "8faf3b77-d510-4c83-8cf3-7972c8af0ec8",
                              "title": "Go 没有锁升级机制",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "207ae0bf-6e2a-4ec1-a927-09e17492ee3b",
                              "title": "Mutex 只有两种模式：正常模式 ⟷ 饥饿模式",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "4382887c-6de6-40cc-a612-6f2eb849e9fb",
                              "title": "正常模式：先自旋几次，失败后阻塞",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "2b737840-d8df-41f1-ba2f-b2c181372f9b",
                              "title": "饥饿模式：直接排队，防止goroutine饿死",
                              "titleUnedited": false,
                              "children": {
                                "attached": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "d8e48fc3-fff8-4c9b-b715-4b6a628bcbec",
                                    "title": "```go\n// Go 的替代方案：根据场景选择不同工具\natomic.AddInt32(&counter, 1)  // 无锁，类似\"轻量级\"\nmu.Lock()                      // 有锁，类似\"重量级\"\n```",
                                    "titleUnedited": false
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "1317af49-ce5f-44ee-916f-6e25685a2fb3",
                        "title": "2. 乐观锁 vs 悲观锁",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "d0082889-45f3-4a7a-8746-dba8d2b3d591",
                              "title": "```go\n// 悲观锁\nmu.Lock()\ncounter++\nmu.Unlock()\n\n// 乐观锁（CAS）\natomic.AddInt32(&counter, 1)\n\n// 手动 CAS 循环\nfor {\n    old := atomic.LoadInt32(&counter)\n    if atomic.CompareAndSwapInt32(&counter, old, old+1) {\n        break\n    }\n}\n```",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "e8bca112-13f1-41f4-8400-9525ef16ae56",
                        "title": "3. 公平锁 vs 非公平锁",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "70e7ae5b-4d90-4161-8053-17d41951ae5a",
                              "title": "```java\nReentrantLock fairLock = new ReentrantLock(true);   // 公平\nReentrantLock unfairLock = new ReentrantLock(false); // 非公平\n```",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "fa69b617-55d0-40ae-a3a4-982f73d96ce9",
                              "title": "**正常模式（类似非公平）**：新来的goroutine可能抢到锁，性能好",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "9af3700e-78a3-4fb1-8e31-509ae957b88a",
                              "title": "**饥饿模式（类似公平）**：等待超过1ms自动切换，锁直接交给队首",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "06486fa7-6dc4-4b28-876c-6f695fc5ac8b",
                        "title": "4. 可重入锁（重要区别！）",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "b82ef830-3c1f-463b-b7b9-2a19679f52b6",
                              "title": "```java\nsynchronized void outer() {\n    inner();  // ✅ 同一线程可重入\n}\nsynchronized void inner() { }\n```",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "78779bb2-f4cd-442a-b76b-5eaf1d9e55af",
                              "title": "```go\nvar mu sync.Mutex\n\nfunc outer() {\n    mu.Lock()\n    defer mu.Unlock()\n    inner()  // 💀 死锁！\n}\n\nfunc inner() {\n    mu.Lock()  // 永远阻塞\n    defer mu.Unlock()\n}\n```",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "853582e8-55dd-4339-90ef-4d86c55a9a16",
                              "title": "```go\n// 方案1：重构代码，内部函数不加锁\nfunc outer() {\n    mu.Lock()\n    defer mu.Unlock()\n    innerLocked()  // 约定：调用者已持有锁\n}\n\nfunc innerLocked() {\n    // 不加锁，假设调用者已持有\n}\n\n// 方案2：拆分锁的粒度\n// 方案3：使用 channel 替代锁\n```",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "c511a792-27a9-4e04-8f74-f37917fab39b",
                        "title": "5. 锁粗化（Lock Coarsening）",
                        "titleUnedited": false,
                        "children": {
                          "attached": [
                            {
                              "id": "d97d0ac0-2061-4a3e-bdfe-06dfac779b39",
                              "title": "```java\n// JIT 会自动把循环内的锁提到循环外\nfor (int i = 0; i < 100; i++) {\n    synchronized (obj) { list.add(i); }\n}\n// 优化为 ↓\nsynchronized (obj) {\n    for (int i = 0; i < 100; i++) { list.add(i); }\n}\n```",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            },
                            {
                              "id": "bd82706a-d7c1-4949-bc5c-513cf8f1cda0",
                              "title": "```go\n// 坏：频繁加锁解锁\nfor i := 0; i < 100; i++ {\n    mu.Lock()\n    list = append(list, i)\n    mu.Unlock()\n}\n\n// 好：手动粗化\nmu.Lock()\nfor i := 0; i < 100; i++ {\n    list = append(list, i)\n}\nmu.Unlock()\n```",
                              "titleUnedited": false
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "baa88270-0de8-4fec-9781-e91c9bf37fdb",
                        "title": "6. Go 没有的 Java 特性",
                        "titleUnedited": false
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "bc0880be-b04d-49db-ad36-076a42296b32",
                        "title": "Go 的设计哲学",
                        "titleUnedited": false
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        ]
